#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:523
msgid "data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_FIGHT_WOF\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You ship has barely finished the jump but you're already in front of a small but furious-looking RK Scorch ship, shouting fast on open comms.\n"
"\t\t\"Here they are! You shouldn't have messed with our deliveries, dirty Merc! Don't even try to deny it. Die! Burn!\"\n"
"\t\tYou do try to tell them that they are mistaken but their guns are quickly warming up as they rush to take you down.\n"
"\n"
"\t\tUnless you have something very convincing to tell them, it seems you'll have to fight!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:533
