msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_FIGHT_WOF\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_rk_defromorius\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"--NEW OBJECTIVE: DEFUSE SITUATION-- Stop. Greetings.\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\"Oh shit they have captured Defromorius! DIE SCU-\" Somebody on the other ship interrupts the captain before he starts firing. \"Don't be an idiot, calm down and look again\" \"What? Wait. Oh. Oh! Sorry sir, I should really chill every now and then to avoid making mistakes like this. Here's an apology. See you around sir!\""

