"\"Oh god dammit, you're with those Zoltan party poopers? Just my luck... I'm not risking our lives over this, come on in.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tAfter a thorough search, you find their RK weaponry! You're supposed to drop it off at a Zoltan Police Station, but keeping it could help with your more important mission."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1507
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_SUSPICIOUS_SMUGGLER\"]/choice[@req=\"RKS_POLICE_WARRANT\""
" and not(@lvl)]/event[2]/choice/text"
msgstr "Nice!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_radikal.xml:1513
