msgid ""
"data/events_sector_radikal.xml$//event[@name=\"RKS_LAB_SCORCH_AMBUSH\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You barely even reach the Jump button as a small Orchid fleet jumps in! A very angry Praetor ship immediately hails you.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\"Federation. Scouts saw you engage with these people. You traitorous pest. We will avenge our people. Then raze this abomination of a planet.\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\tYou wonder why they would expose themselves to weaponry so specifically good against their biology, but your scans reveal they came quite prepared!"

